Generate a 4K 3D animated mockup video.

CATEGORY ANALYSIS & RULES (CRITICAL):
1. IF CLOTHING (Jacket, Shirt, Hoodie):
   - Use INVISIBLE GHOST MANNEQUIN.
   - Hollow clothing form. NO VISIBLE MANNEQUIN. NO BODY PARTS.
